 an ultimate hand-picked collection of best WordPress education themes. However, these are professionally designed and also has outstanding features that help you to create a stunning website. So choose the best one that suits you. For further details check the list  of <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Free WordPress Themes (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.wpentire.com/free-wordpress-themes/\" target=\"_blank\">Free WordPress Themes</a> for educational websites below.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>1. Education Hub </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Education Hub is an elegant, clean, and best <a href=\"https://www.wpentire.com/free-wordpress-themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"free WordPress theme (opens in a new tab)\">free WordPress theme</a> for educational website. While it is certainly a great choice for you if you are looking for a creative and feature-packed theme for your educational based sites. Although this theme is best suited for college, school, university, and other educational websites. The theme is highly customizable and also comes with layout settings and several theme options. Additionally, it helps you to create an intuitively professional website with high resolution. Furthermore, Education Hub is super flexible and customizable so that it takes just a minute to create an awesome website. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Education Hub: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Responsive design </li><li>WordPress live customizer </li><li>Custom header options</li><li>Front page widget area</li><li>Footer widget </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/education-hub/1.9.8/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/education-hub/\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Details</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://demo.wenthemes.com/education-hub/\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>2.  Education Base</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Education Base is another attractive, modern and easy to use free WordPress education theme. Although the theme has responsive design and comes along with colorful design and stunning flexibility. Education Base has advanced theme options and available various widgets with drag and drops features will help to customize your site as you need. In addition, this theme is compatible with WordPress major plugins including WooCommerce and page builder by SiteOrigin. Moreover, you can use it for your online shop or online courses selling, also can create a site using the widgets and drag and drop page builder. This theme will help you to create a high-quality educational website easily with no time at all.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Education Base: &nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>WooCommerce compatible </li><li>Awesome featured section </li><li>Header options</li><li>One page menu</li><li>Colors options </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/education-base/2.0.0/screenshot.jpg?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/education-base/\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Details</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"http://www.acmethemes.com/demo/?theme=education-base\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>3. Enlighten</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Enlighten is also one of the best free WordPress education themes. This theme is ideal for creating a college, school, university, and other academic/educational websites. Although the theme is flexible and versatile which is optimized for all the mobile devices, desktops, etc. Moreover, it is fully customizer based user-friendly theme which allows you to customize most of the theme settings instantly with live real-time live preview. Enlighten is fully mobile-responsive so that your website content is sure to look great on any device. Additionally, this responsive theme is a fully widgetized theme with multiple widget areas. Create a beautiful education website and enlighten the world. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Enlighten: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Fully customizer based theme </li><li>Beautiful homepage slider</li><li>Custom header options</li><li>Carousel service section </li><li>Sidebar options </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/enlighten/1.2.8/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/enlighten/\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Details</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://accesspressthemes.com/theme-demos/?theme=enlighten\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University is another responsive WordPress theme that can be used for educational, academic, institutions or business websites. Although on the front page of the theme, there is a slider where you can feature as many pages or posts as you want. Moreover, this theme also integrated 11 social media icon fonts. In addition, it is fully responsive that offers a fluid layout with a versatile set of features. On the other hand, the University theme also compatible with the latest version of WordPress. And also compatible with all major browsers. Furthermore, the theme features a custom menu system, multi-level dropdown, one widget ready location and many more awesome features that help you to create a stunning website. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of the University: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>100% responsive design </li><li>Feature posts images </li><li>Front page slideshow</li><li>Translation ready</li><li>Social media icons</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/university/1.3/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/university/\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Details</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"http://demo.vivathemes.com/themes/university/\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>5. Preschool and Kindergarten</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Preschool and kindergarten is a beautiful educational WordPress theme suitable for school, academy, institutions, LMS, training center, and other educational institutions. While the theme is highly customizable with various features and personalization options. Additionally, this theme comes with several features to make a user-friendly, interactive and visually stunning website. It is properly tested and optimized for speed and faster page load time and has a secure and clean code. In addition, the stunning theme is also translation ready. Hence this theme has more features like SEO friendly with optimized codes, which make it easy for your site to rank on Google and other search engines. If your preschool, kindergarten, school, college or university needs an online home that is dynamic and multi-functional, then this theme is a good place to start. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Preschool and Kindergarten: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Social media options</li><li>Call to action button</li><li>SEO friendly</li><li>Attractive slider</li><li>Highly customizable</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/preschool-and-kindergarten/1.1.5/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/preschool-and-kindergarten/\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Details</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://demo.raratheme.com/preschool-and-kindergarten/\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>6. Scholarship</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Scholarship, like its name suggests, is a free theme engineered for educational and tutorial websites. While the theme is fully responsive that displays your site in the best possible way on smartphones, tablets, and laptops, as well as large desktop screens. Although this theme has a clean design with powerful features. Thus, Scholarship would be the best choice for anyone with an intent to promote education online. Furthermore, it also sports custom colorization and a retina ready design to make it look very presentable on every platform.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Scholarship: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Responsive design</li><li>Retina ready</li><li>Highly customizable</li><li>Drag and drop section</li><li>Multiple color options</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/scholarship/1.0.9/screenshot.jpg?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/scholarship/\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Details</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"http://demo.mysterythemes.com/scholarship/\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>7. Educenter </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Educenter is yet another an ideal free WordPress education theme. It is a simple, clean, elegant, user-friendly, impressive, engaging, and dynamic WordPress theme. Although this free education WordPress theme is specially designed for the type of education business website. Moreover, Educenter theme allows you to create a very high-quality and perfect instructional website effortlessly and easily in a short time. Additionally, this WordPress theme has several advanced features and layouts settings too. Besides this, this beautiful WordPress education theme is fully responsive, cross-browser compatible, translation ready, and SEO friendly theme. Along with this, the theme comes with several more awesome features. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Educenter: &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Powerful option panel</li><li>Unlimited color options</li><li>Fully optimized and SEO friendly</li><li>WooCommerce compatible</li><li>Browser compatibility</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/educenter/1.1.1/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/educenter/\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Details</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"h