opener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/search/Wp-Insert/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>6. Easy Google Adsense &nbsp;</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Easy Google Adsense plugin is yet another WordPress plugin that makes Google Adsense monetization easier for WordPress. While the plugin will help you put advertisements on your page in a snap of a finger. Although this plugin offers you easy ads management and makes sure that your site doesn’t get banned from the Adsense program by making you stick to their policies. Moreover, with this plugin, there is no need to manually add Adsense ads/code to different parts of your website. You just enter your Google Adsense Publisher ID in the settings and Google will automatically start showing ads at optimal times when they are likely to perform well for your website and provide a good experience for your users.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Easy-Google-Adsense.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-75\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Easy-Google-Adsense.png 983w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Easy-Google-Adsense-300x162.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Easy-Google-Adsense-768x414.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 983px) 100vw, 983px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-google-adsense/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>7. Google Adsense Plugin</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Google Adsense plugin is a superb solution to earn money by placing ads to WordPress website pages, posts, custom posts, search results, categories, tags, and widgets. While the plugin is packed with plenty of useful features, and should more than suffice for your needs. The plugin lets you show different types of ads including text, image, and image ads, link blocks, etc. Furthermore, you will also find several positions for displaying the ads. In addition, you can choose a default color palette to choose custom colors for the ads. There is also the option to add your custom codes using the plugins settings page. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Google-Adsense-Plugin.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-78\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Google-Adsense-Plugin.png 974w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Google-Adsense-Plugin-300x167.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Google-Adsense-Plugin-768x427.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 974px) 100vw, 974px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/adsense-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>8. Quick Adsense </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Quick Adsense is yet another Ads management WordPress plugin that offers a quicker and flexible way to insert Adsense or any Ads code into a blog post. While it is straightforward to use and comes with a simple settings page. With Quick Adsense, you have quite a bunch of different options where you would like to place ads. Moreover, the settings section is user-friendly so everyone gets the most out of Quick Adsense. Additionally, you can also disable ads on the fly and add up to ten advertisements on a page or post. The plugin provides deep integration with video intelligence to provide enhanced features and for easy integration with their services. <br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Quick-Adsense.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-79\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Quick-Adsense.png 994w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Quick-Adsense-300x161.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Quick-Adsense-768x411.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 994px) 100vw, 994px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download  (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-adsense/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>9. Google Adsense In-feed </strong><br></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Google Adsense in Feed is another best WordPress Adsense plugin. Although the plugin has full support for all types of Adsense ads even auto ads. Moreover, it fully supports AMP and caching plugins and shows an alternative ad to those folks who use an ad blocker. In addition, it is dedicated to Google Adsense ad type to monetize overview pages with a highly engaging layout and specialized options. This plugin was developed to place, manage and test ads on pages to increase revenue and usability. Additionally, it support for all Google Adsense types like units, responsive, in-feed, in-article and matched the content. <br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Google-Adsense-In-feed.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-80\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Google-Adsense-In-feed.png 985w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Google-Adsense-In-feed-300x170.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Google-Adsense-In-feed-768x435.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 985px) 100vw, 985px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/advanced-ads-adsense-in-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\">Details + Download</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>10. Adsense In-Post Ads</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Adsense In-Post Ads plugin allows you to save your most used Adsense ads codes and insert them as a shortcode in your pages or posts. This plugin offers you simple shortcode option that you insert in your posts to make sure that you are able to display the advertisements. In addition, it will increase the odds that readers will click on the ad. Furthermore, this plugin also helps you to display your ads in a widgetized area of your pages such as the left or right sidebars, or in the header or footer of your page. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Adsense-In-Post-Ads.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-82\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Adsense-In-Post-Ads.png 984w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Adsense-In-Post-Ads-300x165.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Adsense-In-Post-Ads-768x423.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 984px) 100vw, 984px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/adsense-in-post-ads-by-oizuled/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\">Details + Download</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Wrapping Up </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The above-mentioned plugins are some of the best WordPress Google Adsense Plugins. While these plugins will help you to manage your Adsense ads effectively. We hope you found the list to be useful. Select the best WordPress plugin and maximize the revenue from the blog post. <br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>For more check our latest collection:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/best-free-travel-agency-wordpress-plugins/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Best Travel Agency WordPress Plugins (opens in a new tab)\">Best Travel Agency WordPress Plugins</a></strong><br></p>\n\n\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/best-wordpress-google-adsense-plugins/\">Best WordPress Google Adsense Plugins</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog\">Mantrabrain Blog</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/best-wordpress-google-adsense-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"5+ Best Free Travel Agency WordPress Plugins 2019\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/best-free-travel-agency-wordpress-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://mantrabrain.com