avel-agency-wordpress-plugins/\">5+ Best Free Travel Agency WordPress Plugins 2019</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog\">Mantrabrain Blog</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Kabita Pokharel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12974:\"\n<p>You must be wondering which are the best free travel agency WordPress plugins that suit your travel website. While these plugins will help you to create a whole tour management system online with different features like &#8211; travel booking, easy payment methods and many more. In this competitive market, it is hard to get more customers to increase productivity. To achieve this target most people are using travel agency WordPress plugins on their WordPress sites. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here, in this article, we have listed some best free travel agency WordPress plugins. These free plugins are best and are specific to travel blogs. So these plugins could help you to grow your travel blog faster and more efficiently. &nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yatra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Yatra (opens in a new tab)\">Yatra</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Yatra is powerful WordPress travel booking system. This plugin is designed for travel and tour agency company. It is really easy, fast, flexible plugin. Any one can make tour package easily and can mange frontend tabs within a minute. Another main awesome feature is custom attribute for tour package, you can add custom attribute ( like height, temperature etc) from attribute section of this plugin. You can create unlimited tour packages, custom attribute, activity, destinations without any trouble. If you are running a travel &amp; tour related business and searching for travel booking system in WordPress then this plugin might be best option for you. For your understanding we have listed it&#8217;s features below.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Yatra: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Unlimited travel &amp; tour option</li><li>Activity and destination category for your tour package</li><li>Multiple pricing options ( sales and regular pricing) </li><li>Customizable tabs </li><li>Unlimited Itineraries building </li><li>Unlimited FAQ items</li><li>Awesome custom attributes for your unique tour packages</li><li>Easy interface with user friendly booking report</li><li>Free and fast customer support </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/banner-772x250.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-134\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/banner-772x250.png 772w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/banner-772x250-300x97.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/banner-772x250-768x249.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yatra/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download </a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>WP Travel </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>WP Travel is the best choice for a travel agency. It is scalable, powerful, easy to use the plugin for WordPress to manage packages and booking. Although this plugin is compatible with some of the best travel agency WordPress theme, this is the ultimate travel engine for travel and tour management WordPress websites. Furthermore, WP Travel is one of the most versatile plugins developed by programmers for programmers! Do more than just making a website by using our powerful WP Travel add-ons. It is one of the best tour operator booking engines that is simple and provides all you need to run an online travel and trekking business. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of WP Travel: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Travel site ready </li><li>Full data reporting </li><li>Multiple pricing and multiple dates </li><li>Customizable tabs </li><li>Itineraries booking </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-55\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel.png 978w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel-300x164.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel-768x421.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 978px) 100vw, 978px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-travel/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download </a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Travelpayouts</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Travelpayouts is another travel plugin for WordPress that is easy to install. It provides low price flights, hotels, and calendars. Although it covers the entire range of travel services, including flights, hotels, cars rentals, insurance. Transfers, and much more. Additionally, it also helps your visitors to organize their vacation and increase your earnings. This travel WordPress travel plugin is a very good solution for travel bloggers, travel agencies and travel related websites. Moreover, with this plugin, you can use 11 different customizable tables and 2 customizable tables for hotels. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Travelpayouts: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Low price calendar </li><li>Hotel widget </li><li>2 customizable tables with hotel prices and info</li><li>Popular flight destination widget </li><li>It supports all kind of currencies </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Travelpayouts.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-57\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Travelpayouts.png 982w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Travelpayouts-300x163.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Travelpayouts-768x418.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 982px) 100vw, 982px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/travelpayouts/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>WP Travel Engine</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>WP Travel Engine is a free travel booking WordPress plugin to create travel and tour packages for tour operators and travel agencies. While this plugin is flexible and easy to use. In this plugin, you can create subcategories according to the trip type. Additionally, you can also create a destination page and facts about different places and trips. You can create an infinite number of tour packages. It is a complete travel management system and includes plenty of useful features. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of WP Travel Engine: &nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Unlimited tour packages </li><li>The smart travel booking process</li><li>Translation ready </li><li>Inquiry form </li><li>Payment processing </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel-Engine.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-58\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel-Engine.png 992w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel-Engine-300x163.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel-Engine-768x417.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 992px) 100vw, 992px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-travel-engine/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Travel Agency Companion</strong> </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Travel Agency Companion is yet another free travel agency WordPress plugin. It is a plugin that adds extras functionalities and features to the travel agency theme. Although the plugin when activated installs few widgets and adds extra features on the customizer. Moreover, the Travel Agency Companion plugin adds three very useful customized widgets, namely, featured post widget, popular post widget, and recent post widget. Besides this, the plugin adds extra options for customizing homepage of the travel agency theme. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Travel Agency Companion: &nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Free WordPress Travel Agency Plugin</li><li>Add extra options for customizing homepage</li><li>Featured post widget </li><li>Translation ready </li><li>Flexible and easy to use </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Travel-Agency-Companion.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-61\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Travel-Agency-Companion.png 987w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Travel-Agency-Companion-300x164.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Travel-Agency-Companion-768x419.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/travel-agency-companion/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>WP Booking</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>WP Booking is a WordPress plugin that creates a fully complete booking system. Although the plugin gives you a complete solution for making any kind of booking and reservation site you can imagine. Furthermore, WP Booking provides a complete system for effortlessly building a booking and reservation site especially created for you. It is fully responsive and SEO friendly WordPress plugin. In addition, the plugin is translated into many different languages. It is also a developer-friendly WordPress plugin. a</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of WP Booking: &nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Multiple payment systems </li><li>Responsive design </li><li>SEO friendly plugin </li><li>Translation ready </li><li>Developer friendly </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Booking.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-62\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Booking.png 985w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Booking-300x140.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Booking-768x358.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 985px) 100vw, 985px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-booking-management-system/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>WP Travel MapQuest </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>WP Travel MapQuest is a map display plugin which is a fantastic way of showing your business location. While this plugin can replace the use of Google map with its own features of locating the desired locations. In addition, this plugin can also be used to search the locations by using the latitude and longitude values or directly with the “start searching” option. It is a simple map addon to WP travel plugin which can be used in place of Google map. Additionally, it is very flexible and highly customizable WordPress plugin. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of WP Travel MapQuest: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Zoom level setting </li><li>Search feature </li><li>Flexible and highly customizable</li><li>Easy to set up</li><li>And more under development…</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel-MapQuest.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-64\" srcset=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel-MapQuest.png 983w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel-MapQuest-300x164.png 300w, https://mantrabrain.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/WP-Travel-MapQuest-768x420.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 983px) 100vw, 983px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-travel-mapquest/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Wrapping Up</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In this post, I have listed 5+ best free travel agency WordPress plugins for your tour and travel website. We hope these plugins will help you in attracting new customers and increase your productivity. <br></p>\n\n\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/best-free-travel-agency-wordpress-plugins/\">5+ Best Free Travel Agency WordPress Plugins 2019</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog\