19</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog\">Mantrabrain Blog</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Kabita Pokharel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22214:\"\n<p>Are you looking for free WordPress travel themes that are suitable for your travel website? Perfect, you are in the right place. While there are lots of themes on WordPress. If you want to create a travel website, you can find much amazing WordPress travel themes. Hence these all themes are fully free to use and also have awesome features.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are lots of powerful themes on WordPress that can be convenient options to create a travel-related website. So that we would like to present to you our unique and prominent collection of best free WordPress travel themes. However, all the free WordPress travel themes in the list are yet most popular and the best ones. Here we have handpicked these best themes for suitable for your travel website. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>1. Travel Eye </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Travel Eye is a clean and professional looking travel WordPress theme. The theme is ideal for crafting travel agencies, hotels, tours or any other organization related to travel and tours. While you can easily enable parallax effects, cool drop-down menus and custom widgets using this theme. Additionally, the full-screen slider gives you all the screen real state you need to captivate your audience with stunning pictures. This theme is completely SEO friendly so it will create a positive result for your site in a google search. Furthermore, the theme comes with a prebuilt layout with great sections that elegantly perfect the design. Thus, Travel Eye is one of the best looking free WordPress travel themes out there. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Travel Eye: &nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Parallax options </li><li>Custom CSS options </li><li>Multiple menus</li><li>Responsive design</li><li>Footer widgets &nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/travel-eye/1.7.2/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/travel-eye/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wenthemes.com/theme-demos/?demo=travel-eye\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>2. Catch Kathmandu</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Catch Kathmandu is an elegantly designed travel WordPress theme. It is a fully responsive, clean and lightweight WordPress theme. Although this theme lets you easily customize a wide range of theme options, ranging from layouts to colors to footers and headers, menu and more. Moreover, the theme has a retina ready design that makes it run perfectly on all resolutions. This theme is widely been used by photographers, bloggers, corporate houses and universities. Furthermore, Catch Kathmandu themes design is highly customizable and you can also tailor the display to your taste with a few easy clicks. This complete WordPress travel theme is built to make your travel website shine. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Catch Kathmandu: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Feature post slider </li><li>Custom widgets </li><li>Webmasters tools</li><li>Responsive design</li><li>Color options</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/catch-kathmandu/3.9.7/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/catch-kathmandu/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://catchthemes.com/demo/catch-kathmandu/\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>3. Travel Diaries</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Travel Diaries is yet another free WordPress travel themes. Travel Diaries provide you with a clean and easily manageable blog layout perfect for the modern-day adventurer. Although the theme comes with a clean and well organized, responsive layout and multiple customization options. The charismatic outlook of the theme will give your site a crisp and simple look. Moreover, this theme is great looking and beautiful theme with features like it is possible to add your site logo, custom CSS, translation ready, SEO optimized and much more. It&#8217;s custom homepage also comes with tons of cool sections for your blogs. In addition, the theme comes with more powerful features. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Travel Diaries: &nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Highly customizable WordPress theme</li><li>Social media integration</li><li>Cross browser compatible</li><li>Translation ready</li><li>Responsive design</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/travel-diaries/1.1.3/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/travel-diaries/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://demo.raratheme.com/travel-diaries/\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. Swing Lite </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Swing Lite is a beautiful Hotel WordPress Template, specifically designed to showcase your hospitality industry like hotel, resort, accommodation, and rooms for rent.  The showcase of your unique accommodation is easier with the theme’s beautiful design, and high coding quality which attracts more visitors to your website. The template is compatible with WP hotel booking plugin for booking hotels and rooms, it is also versatile to be used with Corporate and Agency Websites. Moreover, there are three beautiful header layouts available, beautiful slider at the front page with the option of unlimited slides, also the hotel rooms can be displayed either in grid or list layout. The whole theme can also be translated into any language of your choice.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Key features of Swing Lite:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Live Preview in Customizer</li><li>Background Configuration</li><li>Fully SEO optimized</li><li>Fast loading</li><li>Cross browser compatible</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/swing-lite/1.1.2/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/swing-lite/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a>     <a class=\"button\" href=\"https://demo.accesspressthemes.com/swing-lite/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\">Demo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>5. VW Tour Lite</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>VW Tour Lite is another free responsive multipurpose WordPress theme which is ideal for tour and travel website. While it is suitable for travel agency website, traveling or journey blog, tourism, hotels, travelers and many more. By using this theme, you can create an informative, eye-catching and engaging tour and travel websites. Since it supports a wide range of plugins, you can do many things on your website and advance its functionalities. Moreover, the theme is cross-browser compatible and performs well with any browser. Due to its secure and clean code, even the non-coders find it very easy to use. Although it is an SEO friendly theme with optimized codes that helps your site to get a higher rank on Google and other search engines. Hence, it is certain that your website s going to have a good ranking in Google search.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of VW Tour Lite: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Fully responsiveness</li><li>Social media links</li><li>Slider settings</li><li>Theme customization</li><li>Compatible with the latest version of WordPress</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/vw-tour-lite/1.1.3.8/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details + Download (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/vw-tour-lite/\" target=\"_blank\">Details + Download</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.vwthemes.net/vw-tours-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>6. Travelers</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Travelers is a stunning and creative WordPress theme built with Bootstrap and can be considered as the best free WordPress travel theme. With this theme, you can be assured to make a cool website with awesome features. Although the demo data can be installed with just one click in a few minutes and make your site just like in the demo. Furthermore, the theme is search engin