og\">Mantrabrain Blog</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Kabita Pokharel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21149:\"\n<p>Best Free WordPress Magazine Themes helps you to create an awesome website. WordPress is the best platform to find the best WordPress themes for your brand new website. Nowadays magazine websites are popular and provide one of the quality content to viewers. While online magazine websites deliver quality content and adapt to the current social and marketing trends. A good magazine theme gives you a technical ground to build an online presence. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Furthermore, there are lots of paid as well as free magazine themes on WordPress that can be perfect for your magazine websites. Here we have listed some beautiful free magazine WordPress themes. Each one is beautiful in its own way and since they are free so that you can experiment them before selecting one perfect for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"mce_3\"><strong>1. MantraNews</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mantra News theme is reliable, simple, and beautiful free WordPress magazine theme. The theme comes with an attractive layout with different widgets and lots of beautiful features. The themes beautiful design and awesome features helps you to create a stunning magazine website. Although this theme is translation ready and also you can get an awesome featured slider widget. While there are different widgets area on the theme. You can also customize those widgets area. Additionally, this theme is fully responsive that looks great on all type of screens including desktops, tablets, iPhones, smartphones as well as small cellphones. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Furthermore, you can get a lot of options on the header of this theme. The theme is also lightweight and SEO friendly making sure that users are left with a lasting impression. While it is a free theme, yet offers plenty of beautiful features. In addition, it is easy to use and a perfect theme for news portal, creative blogs and any kind of informative websites. It also includes theme color customization options, carousel options, news ticker options, and many more awesome features.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://mantrabrain.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2019/01/screenshot1-1024x768.png\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download+Demo+Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://mantrabrain.com/downloads/mantranews-wordpress-news-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Download+Demo</a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a class=\"button\" href=\"https://mantrabrain.com/downloads/mantranews-wordpress-news-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Details</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>2. CoverNews &nbsp; </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cover News is a clean and elegant free professional looking WordPress theme that is perfect for an <g class=\"gr_ gr_6 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"6\" data-gr-id=\"6\">online</g> blog and magazine. The theme is fully responsive that looks perfect on all screen sizes from small to large devices. It is flexible and adaptable, easily adjust any element to match your preference. Moreover, it is also compatible with WooCommerce plugin that helps you to integrate an online business with your blog easily. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, with the help of this theme, you can add feature post on the banner section. It also has 3 color options for the users to choose and the whole site is SEO friendly that helps to rank your website in the top of search engines. In addition, other useful features of this amazing theme are custom widgets, footer widgets section, post carousel widget, pixel-perfect design and cross-browser compatible and many more. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/covernews/1.2.2/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://afthemes.com/products/covernews/\" target=\"_blank\">Download+Demo</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/covernews/\" target=\"_blank\">Details</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>3. FlyMag &nbsp; </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>FlyMag is a clean, beautiful and responsive magazine style WordPress theme. The theme has a multipurpose and clean design with good coding. While this theme offers a variety of widgets which allows you to create interactive and beautiful magazine site. It has a minimalist yet interactive look with draggable carousel sliders and a visual-friendly appearance overall. Moreover, this theme offers a variety of widgets which allow you to create an interactive and beautiful magazine site.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p>While, the theme makes beautiful use of featured images so your posts will be presented with nice featured mages. Even though this theme is fully responsive and well optimized mobile, tablets and smartphones. So that the content looks great on all devices. In addition, Fly Mag lets you use any of the 600+ Google fonts, provide color options for lot of the theme elements and also offer you some useful page templates. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/flymag/2.0.6