agazine theme<strong>. </strong>It offers strong colors for standing out from the rest of your competition. It comes with a featured content slider and a magazine page template. In addition, the theme provides plenty of features and options that enable you to create professional looking magazine themes. It also offers beautiful slider options to show your featured posts, header search and social icons and a complete magazine homepage. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moreover, Dynamic News Lite is a fully responsive magazine style WordPress theme with bold colors and fonts. The theme has a beautiful flat design and full-width template. Also, it has many features like social icons, custom background, custom header image, strong colors, bold typography and many more. Thus, this best free WordPress theme helps you to create the professional looking news and magazine website in no time.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/dynamic-news-lite/1.6/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://themezee.com/themes/dynamicnews/\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Demo</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/dynamic-news-lite/\" target=\"_blank\">Details</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>8. PT Magazine &nbsp;</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>PT Magazine is another modern looking and perfectly crafted responsive magazine theme. This is a <g class=\"gr_ gr_11 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"11\" data-gr-id=\"11\">beautifully</g> crafted SEO friendly theme. Although the theme can be used for any kind of news and magazine sites. The theme has an elegant design that helps to create simple, minimal, and attractive looks of your website. Thus this free magazine theme is easy to use, fast loading and secure. The theme is based on customizer, widgets, and addon to customize everything you needed. &nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moreover, the theme is fully responsive that looks great on every device. You can also change the site color with just a single click. Additionally, the theme comes with more powerful features. The theme comes with drag and drops widget sections, customizable header, advanced blog settings custom menu and more powerful features. The theme also has color options, social icons and many more. In addition, PT magazine also consists of an overwhelming number of color options to choose from. Overall we can say that PT Magazine can be one of the best choices for your magazine website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/pt-magazine/1.1.2/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.prodesigns.com/wordpress-themes/downloads/pt-magazine\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Demo</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/pt-magazine/\" target=\"_blank\">Details</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>9. Madd Magazine  </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Madd Magazine is a beautiful, unique and responsive WordPress magazine theme. It comes with a built-in responsive slider that lets you integrate image or videos onto your site. It also comes with left and right sidebar to add your favorite widgets. While the theme is simple to use and easy to set up. Furthermore, it has space for advertising, slideshows and other widgets by choice. It also supports several sliders and button colors. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, the theme is lightweight and SEO friendly to give your website the professional magazine look. On the other hand, this theme is also cross-browser compatible which, means that your site will work and look awesome no matter what browser the users decide to use. The Madd Magazine theme comes with Google fonts for the best typography, menus capability, theme options, and many other powerful features. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/madd-magazine/1.0.8/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://dessign.net/madd-magazine/?ref=226\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Demo</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/madd-magazine/\" target=\"_blank\">Details</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>10. VMagazine Lite</strong>  </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>VMagazine Lite is free Multi Layout News Magazine theme for newspaper, magazine and blog websites. The theme has been carefully crafted with elegant designs and great attention to detail. Also with highly configurable theme, VMagazine Lite uses SiteOrigin Page builder which allows you to add your advertisement anywhere you like and 8 built-in widgets to help you create your desired website with ease and perfection.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>VMagazine Lite theme features live ajax search making your website more modern and interesting for the users. Theme color can be changed with the color option according to your design and requirements. Additionally, the theme is fully compatible with the WooCommerce plugin and fully SEO optimized. The whole theme can be translated into a new language helping you to work with ease.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/vmagazine-lite/1.2.0/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://accesspressthemes.com/wordpress-themes/vmagazine-lite/\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Demo</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/vmagazine-lite/\" target=\"_blank\">Details</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>11. HitMag</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>HitMag is a stylish and powerful theme crafted for magazines, newspapers or personal blogs. It comes with a handful of options to customize your site the way you want. Although the theme provides four different layouts to list your blog posts. Additionally, theme layouts include multiple color options to establish your brand. And it also gives the options to select sidebar and content alignment for the blog, posts, and pages globally and internally. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, the theme includes a full-width template, just in case you’d like to clear out the clutter and focus on more of a landing page layout. Along with this, the theme comes with more powerful features like author details box, related posts after articles and control post metadata. It also includes a grid layout, right sidebar, and two column support that helps to look pretty good theme for magazine types. Therefore it is a perfect theme for building beautiful magazine websites. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/hitmag/1.2.2/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://themezhut.com/themes/hitmag/\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Demo</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hitmag/\" target=\"_blank\">Details</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong> 12. Rubine Lite </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Rubine Lite is yet another clean and awesome magazine style free WordPress theme by ThemeZee. The theme offers a gorgeous featured content area on the home page to highlight your most important posts. While the theme is fully responsive that makes your device readable on every device. Furthermore, the theme includes a social media icon so that your visitors can follow your posts in social media networks. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moreover, the theme has more powerful features like a full-width template, custom header image, custom menus, theme customizer and many more. The theme has built-in support for the WP Subtitle Plugin, which makes it super easy to add subtitles to your posts. Just install the plugin and you’re ready to go. In addition, Rubine Lite is licensed under GPL, that means you can use it on unlimited websites for private and commercial purposes. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/themes.svn.wordpress.org/rubine-lite/1.5/screenshot.png?w=1142&amp;strip=all\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Download + Demo (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://themezee.com/themes/rubine/\" target=\"_blank\">Download + Demo</a>     <a class=\"button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Details (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/rubine-lite/\" target=\"_blank\">Details</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Wrapping Up </strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are so many awesome WordPress magazine themes on WordPress. Here we have listed some best themes to make your task easier. These amazing themes are completing free to use and also has powerful features. <br></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/free-wordpress-magazine-themes/\">10+ Best Free WordPress Magazine Themes 2019</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog\">Mantrabrain Blog</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/free-wordpress-magazine-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:34:\"https://mantrabrain.com/blog/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"\n	1	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:15:{s:6:\"server\";s:5:\"nginx\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Thu, 25 Jul 2019 20:54:21 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:14:\"content-length\";s:5:\